      • timeouts

        public ClusteringServiceConfigurationBuilder timeouts(Timeouts timeouts)
        Adds timeouts. Read operations which time out return a result comparable to a cache miss. Write operations which time out won't do anything. Lifecycle operations which time out will fail with exception
        Parameters:
        timeouts - the amount of time permitted for all operations
        Returns:
        a clustering service configuration builder
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if timeouts is null
